nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andy-Burnahm-Manchester-Mayor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andy-Burnahm-Manchester-Mayor-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andy-Burnahm-Manchester-Mayor-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>曼彻斯特市长安迪·伯纳姆（Andy Burnham）在该市首届<a href="https://beyondthemusic.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“超越音乐”会议</a>后接受<em>《NME》</em>采访，表示他希望此次会议能够“激励”音乐产业，因为影响音乐产业的问题在威斯敏斯特“充耳不闻”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brexit-touring-uk-house-of-lords-2022-artist-crew-unemployment-europe-3315337">英国脱欧：英国政府警告音乐家和工作人员“可能会发现自己集体失业”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月的《超越音乐》探讨了音乐行业目前面临的多重危机，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grassroots-venues-need-action-not-kind-words-as-they-had-for-disaster-without-arena-investment-3515347">草根场所的未来</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-burnham-slams-ridiculous-brexit-rules-demands-free-exchange-artists-through-europe-3515357">英国脱欧对艰难前往欧洲巡演的英国音乐家的持续影响</a>。</p><p>关于后者，伯纳姆表示，年轻音乐家的职业生涯仍然受到影响，因为他们在英国脱欧后的欧洲巡演中继续面临困难，这是“完全错误的”。</p><p>在十月份的会议上，伯纳姆讨论了针对艺术家在欧洲各地旅行的“荒谬”的英国脱欧规则。早在 2021 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-industry-feel-theyve-been-dealt-a-no-deal-brexit-but-call-on-government-to-take-it-seriously-and-fix-it-2856716">英国音乐产业就公开表示，</a>当政府<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/government-rejects-visa-free-brexit-touring-petition-blames-eu-promises-help-navigate-changes-2875506">未能就音乐家和工作人员的免签证旅行和欧洲范围内的工作许可证进行谈判</a>时，他们实际上是如何遭遇“无协议脱欧”的。</p><p>尽管试图向部长们提出这些问题，但伯纳姆告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，政府仍然“充耳不闻”，因为政府继续忽视英国脱欧造成的混乱，因为艺术家们正在努力克服在欧洲表演的“各种隐藏障碍”。</p><p> “这太令人沮丧了，特别是考虑到欧洲提供了更好的安排，但在英国脱欧的言论中，它被拒绝了，”他解释说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ministers-reject-fighting-for-visa-free-brexit-touring-plan-for-musicians-2860053">指的是鲍里斯·约翰逊拒绝了欧洲提出的艺术家交易</a>。 “这只是错误的。这个行业对于英国对“UK-plc”的价值来说是巨大的，而且对于它的外交和文化价值以及人们与英国建立积极联系的方式也是如此。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CyV4GMVt_3j/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058,72.155 560.06,72.803 558.662,73.347 C